The '''''Xucphra Meander''''' was one of three [[Bacta Tanker|bacta tankers]] that was hijacked by the former members of [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]] during the [[Ambush of the bacta tankers]], as part of their strategy of [[Bacta War|deposing]] the former head of [[Imperial Intelligence/Legends|Imperial Intelligence]], [[Ysanne Isard]], from her rule of [[Thyferra/Legends|Thyferra]]. Belonging to a small convoy escorted by the [[Victory II-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Victory II''-class Star Destroyer]] [[Corrupter/Legends|''Corrupter'']], after having surrendered, the ship agreed to carry its [[Bacta/Legends|bacta]] to [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. During the trip it was escorted by [[Rhysati Ynr]], [[Inyri Forge]] and two [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]]-[[Pilot/Legends|piloted]] [[Chir'daki]] [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]].

